---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="HOME">
  <section style="background: var(--ok-blue); color: white; padding: 100px 20px; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-weight: 900; font-size: 3.5rem; color: white; margin: 0;">LIGHT ON THE HILL</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 20px auto;">Connecting Louisville to the energy and love of Christ.</p>
  </section>

  <section style="padding: 60px 20px; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; align-items: start;">
      <div>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ok-blue); font-weight: 900;">COMMUNITY MATTERS</h2>
        <p>Whether we're gathering for breakfast at 9:30 AM or exploring local favorites in Louisville, we believe life is better together[cite: 615].</p>
        <div style="height: 4px; width: 60px; background: var(--ok-yellow); margin-top: 20px;"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div style="background: var(--ok-cream); padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; border-right: 8px solid var(--ok-yellow);">
         <h3 style="font-weight: 900; margin-top: 0;">LATEST MESSAGE</h3>
         <p>Our sermon archive is updated weekly with messages that empower and inspire.</p>
         <a href="/sermons" style="color: var(--ok-blue); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;">Watch Library â†’</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
